OL,5, Sir Ed Davey was advised as postal     
OL,6, minister in 2010 to meet Post Office   
OL,7, campaigner Alan Bates to avoid bad     
OL,8, publicity over the Horizon scandal, the
OL,9, BBC has discovered.                    
OL,11,FSir Ed, now Lib Dem leader, has faced  
OL,12,Fquestions in recent weeks over why he  
OL,13,Finitially refused to do so.            
OL,15,FHe did meet the campaigner five months 
OL,16,Flater, and has said he regrets not     
OL,17,Fdoing so sooner.                       
OL,19,FDocuments show he was advised to meet  
OL,20,FMr Bates for "presentational reasons". 
